Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Review Derivatives: Concepts, rules, implicit differentiation, related rates. Practice 3-4 problems.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Practice Mixed Derivatives & Integrals: Work on problems that require distinguishing between derivative and integral applications.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Study Volume of Revolution (Shell Method): Concepts, setup, and solve problems using the cylindrical shell method. Practice 2-3 problems.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Comprehensive Concept Review: Create a summary sheet of key formulas, theorems, and common pitfalls for all topics.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Solve Challenging Multi-Concept Problems: Focus on problems combining 2+ concepts (e.g., L'Hopital's with limits from integral bounds, volumes with complex functions). Practice 3-4 advanced problems.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Targeted Practice & Error Analysis: Review all previous practice problems, identify areas of weakness, and do extra problems specifically on those topics.

Title: Calculus Midterm
Description: Full Mock Midterm Exam: Take a timed, simulated midterm exam (e.g., a past exam or a set of 6-7 mixed problems). Afterwards, review solutions and identify remaining weak spots.
